Revision history for Perl extension XML::Filter::XML_Directory_2XHTML

1.3.1	 Mon Jul 22 2002

	 - Upped required version of XML::Filter::XML_Directory_2::Base to 1.4.4
	 
1.3	 Mon Jul 08 2002

	 - Added $pkg->set_style()

	 - Upped required version of XML::Filter::XML_Directory_2::Base to 1.4.2

	 - Updated POD

1.2.1	 Sun Jul 07 2002

	 - Upped required version of XML::Filter::XML_Directory_2::Base to 1.4.1
	 
1.2	 Fri Jul 05 2002

	 - Added options for passing a code reference to $pkg->set_images()

	 - Upped required version of XML::Filter::XML_Directory_2::Base to 1.4

	 - Updated Makefile.PL accordingly

	 - Updated POD

1.1	 Wed Jul 03 2002

	 - Added $pkg->set_lang()

	 - Updated <head> handler to be more discreet about what the default document title should be. Now prints current location relative to directory root or the basename for the document root itself.

	 - Upped required version for XML::Filter::XML_Directory_2XHTML

1.0	 Tue Jul 02 2002

	 - Initial revision
